  "response": "Here are some affordable and effective ways to learn Spanish:\n\n1. Free/Low-Cost Options:\n- Duolingo (free language learning app)\n- YouTube Spanish learning channels\n- Language exchange websites/apps like Tandem\n- Podcasts (Coffee Break Spanish, SpanishPod101)\n\n2. Online Resources:\n- Memrise\n- Busuu\n- SpanishDict\n- Language learning websites with free content\n\n3. Affordable Methods:\n- Community college classes\n- Online courses on platforms like Coursera or edX\n- Language learning books from library/used bookstores\n- Netflix shows with Spanish audio/subtitles\n\n4. Immersion Techniques:\n- Change device/phone language to Spanish\n- Watch Spanish movies/TV shows\n- Listen to Spanish music\n- Find Spanish conversation partners online\n\n5. Budget-Friendly Practice:\n- Language exchange meetups\n- Practice with native speakers online\n- Use free language learning apps daily\n- Follow Spanish social media accounts\n\n6. Low-Cost Advanced Learning:\n- Conversation exchange websites\n- Language learning Discord/Reddit communities\n- Cheap online tutoring platforms like iTalki\n\nConsistency and daily practice are key to learning Spanish effectively and affordably.",
